Description: A collection of functions for detecting and analyzing rare events
    in datasets. Includes implementations of various anomaly detection methods
    such as isolation forest, DBSCAN clustering, and residual-based approaches.
    Provides tools for spatial point matching, time series extraction, and
    statistical testing for rare event patterns.
